text: maryamara putra masiharu allahana dutarallade berenalla. Avariginta hindeyu devadutariddaru. Avara tayi (maryam) tumba satyavanta mahileyagiddaru. Avaribbaru ahara sevisuttiddaru. Navu yava ritiyalli avarige puravegalannu vivarisikoduttiddevembudannu nodiri mattu (istagiyu) avaru ellello aleyuttiruvudannu nodiri
